{{Cut|Star Wars: Empire at War}}
The '''''Twi'lek Dancer''''' was an [[Interceptor IV-class frigate|''Interceptor IV''-class Frigate]] in the service of [[Tyber Zann]] and the [[Zann Consortium/Legends|Zann Consortium]]. Unlike most ships in its class, the ''Twi'lek Dancer'' made use of a [[Cloaking device/Legends|cloaking device]] to give it an added level of defense against detection.

==Behind the scenes==
The ''Twi'lek Dancer'' was cut from the game ''[[Star Wars: Empire at War: Forces of Corruption]]''.

